OL,7,FEverton have confirmed a proposed
OL,8,Ftakeover of the club by The Friedkin
OL,9,FGroup, who have agreed to purchase
OL,10,FFarhad Moshiri's majority stake in the
OL,11,Fclub.
OL,13,FThe group, led by the American
OL,14,Fbillionaire Dan Friedkin, had entered
OL,15,Fa period of exclusivity to negotiate a
OL,16,Fpossible purchase in June, before
OL,17,FEverton in July said that no deal
OL,18,Fwould be struck between the parties.
