OL,7,FBut in a statement released on Monday,
OL,8,Fa spokesperson said: "Blue Heaven
OL,9,FHoldings and The Friedkin Group
OL,10,Fconfirm that they have reached
OL,11,Fagreement over the terms of the sale
OL,12,Fof Blue Heaven Holdings' majority
OL,13,Fstake in Everton Football Club.
OL,15,F"The transaction is subject to
OL,16,Fregulatory approval, including from
OL,17,Fthe Premier League, the Football
OL,18,FAssociation, and the Financial Conduct
OL,19,FAuthority."
