OL,7,FA spokesperson for The Friedkin Group
OL,8,Fsaid: "We are pleased to have reached
OL,9,Fan agreement to become custodians of
OL,10,Fthis iconic football club.
OL,12,F"We are focused on securing the
OL,13,Fnecessary approvals to complete the
OL,14,Ftransaction. We look forward to
OL,15,Fproviding stability to the club, and
OL,16,Fsharing our vision for its future,
OL,17,Fincluding the completion of the new
OL,18,FEverton Stadium at Bramley-Moore Dock."
